  </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <p>How did\n      you do? Know that you learn more from wrong answers than from right\n      answers! Wrong answers help us find flaws in our thinking. Take a minute\n      to think about why you got the question wrong. Then you won&rsquo;t get this\n      type of question wrong again!</p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
